headline: Drugmakers are pouring billions of dollars into new US manufacturing. It still won’t achieve all of Trump’s tariff goals
summary: Ever since President Donald Trump started promising to slap tariffs on pharmaceutical imports, drugmakers have unveiled a flurry of commitments to build or expand US manufacturing operations in the coming years.

headline: Walt Disney, McDonald's, Palantir Set To Report Earnings
summary: Key earnings this week will include PLTR, ON, AMD, CAT, & PFE. With Trump's revised tariff orders, investors will be keeping an eye on economic reports releasing next week.
